rows.label: tlk42350116_01_msg0001
rows.name:
I don't think this is
the time for a detour.

rows.label: tlk42350116_01_msg0002
rows.name:
Ah, so busy, so busy, mo!
So many customers, mo!

rows.label: tlk42350116_01_msg0003
rows.name:
Chanopon, a huge hit even with
the merchants who come to
Avaritia, is now on sale, mo!

rows.label: tlk42350116_01_msg0004
rows.name:
But right now, there are so many
customers, I can't get away, mo!

rows.label: tlk42350116_01_msg0005
rows.name:
So if you want to buy Chanopon,
you should come at night when
it's not so busy, mo!

rows.label: tlk42350116_01_msg0006
rows.name:
You're quite the savvy customer
to come during the less busy
hours at night, mo.

rows.label: tlk42350116_01_msg0007
rows.name:
So delicious you'll be
hooked after one bite! Want
to buy some Chanopon, mo?

rows.label: tlk42350116_01_msg0008
rows.name:
Thanks for your business, mo. I added
some extra veggies for you, mo.

rows.label: tlk42350116_01_msg0010
rows.name:
When you get hungry, you should
come and eat Chanopon, mo.

rows.label: tlk42350116_01_msg0011
rows.name:
Owner, mo! Chanopon is as
popular as ever today, mo!
